1359 static void MmwDemo_mboxReadTask(UArg arg0, UArg arg1)
1360 {
1361  MmwDemo_message message;
1362  int32_t retVal = 0;
1363  uint32_t totalPacketLen;
1364  uint32_t numPaddingBytes;
1365  uint32_t itemIdx;
1366 
1367  /* wait for new message and process all the messages received from the peer */
1368  while(1)
1369  {
1370  Semaphore_pend(gMmwMssMCB.mboxSemHandle, BIOS_WAIT_FOREVER);
1371 
1372  /* Read the message from the peer mailbox: We are not trying to protect the read
1373  * from the peer mailbox because this is only being invoked from a single thread */
1374  retVal = Mailbox_read(gMmwMssMCB.peerMailbox, (uint8_t*)&message, sizeof(MmwDemo_message));
1375  if (retVal < 0)
1376  {
1377  /* Error: Unable to read the message. Setup the error code and return values */
1378  System_printf ("Error: Mailbox read failed [Error code %d]\n", retVal);
1379  }
1380  else if (retVal == 0)
1381  {
1382  /* We are done: There are no messages available from the peer execution domain. */
1383  continue;
1384  }
1385  else
1386  {
1387  /* Flush out the contents of the mailbox to indicate that we are done with the message. This will
1388  * allow us to receive another message in the mailbox while we process the received message. */
1389  Mailbox_readFlush (gMmwMssMCB.peerMailbox);
1390 
1391  /* Process the received message: */
1392  switch (message.type)
1393  {
1394  case MMWDEMO_DSS2MSS_DETOBJ_READY:
1395  /* Got detetced objectes , shipped out through UART */
1396  /* Send header */
1397  totalPacketLen = sizeof(MmwDemo_output_message_header);
1398  UART_writePolling (gMmwMssMCB.loggingUartHandle,
1399  (uint8_t*)&message.body.detObj.header,
1400  sizeof(MmwDemo_output_message_header));
1401 
1402  /* Send TLVs */
1403  for (itemIdx = 0; itemIdx < message.body.detObj.header.numTLVs; itemIdx++)
1404  {
1405  UART_writePolling (gMmwMssMCB.loggingUartHandle,
1406  (uint8_t*)&message.body.detObj.tlv[itemIdx],
1407  sizeof(MmwDemo_output_message_tl));
1408  UART_writePolling (gMmwMssMCB.loggingUartHandle,
1409  (uint8_t*)SOC_translateAddress(message.body.detObj.tlv[itemIdx].address,
1410  SOC_TranslateAddr_Dir_FROM_OTHER_CPU,NULL),
1411  message.body.detObj.tlv[itemIdx].length);
1412  totalPacketLen += sizeof(MmwDemo_output_message_tl) + message.body.detObj.tlv[itemIdx].length;
1413  }
1414 
1415  /* Send padding to make total packet length multiple of MMWDEMO_OUTPUT_MSG_SEGMENT_LEN */
1416  numPaddingBytes = MMWDEMO_OUTPUT_MSG_SEGMENT_LEN - (totalPacketLen & (MMWDEMO_OUTPUT_MSG_SEGMENT_LEN-1));
1417  if (numPaddingBytes<MMWDEMO_OUTPUT_MSG_SEGMENT_LEN)
1418  {
1419  uint8_t padding[MMWDEMO_OUTPUT_MSG_SEGMENT_LEN];
1420  /*DEBUG:*/ memset(&padding, 0xf, MMWDEMO_OUTPUT_MSG_SEGMENT_LEN);
1421  UART_writePolling (gMmwMssMCB.loggingUartHandle,
1422  padding,
1423  numPaddingBytes);
1424  }
1425 
1426  /* Send a message to MSS to log the output data */
1427  memset((void *)&message, 0, sizeof(MmwDemo_message));
1428 
1429  message.type = MMWDEMO_MSS2DSS_DETOBJ_SHIPPED;
1430 
1431  if (MmwDemo_mboxWrite(&message) != 0)
1432  {
1433  System_printf ("Error: Mailbox send message id=%d failed \n", message.type);
1434  }
1435 
1436  break;
1437  case MMWDEMO_DSS2MSS_STOPDONE:
1438  /* Post event that stop is done */
1439  gMmwMssMCB.stats.dssSensorStop++;
1440  Event_post(gMmwMssMCB.eventHandleNotify, MMWDEMO_DSS_STOP_COMPLETED_EVT);
1441  break;
1442  case MMWDEMO_DSS2MSS_ASSERT_INFO:
1443  /* Send the received DSS assert info through CLI */
1444  CLI_write ("DSS Exception: %s, line %d.\n", message.body.assertInfo.file,
1445  message.body.assertInfo.line);
1446  break;
1447  case MMWDEMO_DSS2MSS_ISR_INFO_ADDRESS:
1448  gMmwMssMCB.dss2mssIsrInfoAddress =
1449  SOC_translateAddress(message.body.dss2mssISRinfoAddress,
1450  SOC_TranslateAddr_Dir_FROM_OTHER_CPU, NULL);
1451  MmwDemo_installDss2MssExceptionSignallingISR();
1452  break;
1453  case MMWDEMO_DSS2MSS_MEASUREMENT_INFO:
1454  /* Send the received DSS calibration info through CLI */
1455  CLI_write ("compRangeBiasAndRxChanPhase");
1456  CLI_write (" %.7f", message.body.compRxChanCfg.rangeBias);
1457  int32_t i;
1458  for (i = 0; i < SYS_COMMON_NUM_TX_ANTENNAS*SYS_COMMON_NUM_RX_CHANNEL; i++)
1459  {
1460  CLI_write (" %.5f", (float) message.body.compRxChanCfg.rxChPhaseComp[i].real/32768.);
1461  CLI_write (" %.5f", (float) message.body.compRxChanCfg.rxChPhaseComp[i].imag/32768.);
1462  }
1463  CLI_write ("\n");
1464  break;
1465  default:
1466  {
1467  /* Message not support */
1468  System_printf ("Error: unsupport Mailbox message id=%d\n", message.type);
1469  break;
1470  }
1471  }
1472  }
1473  }
1474 }

1986 void MmwDemo_mssCtrlPathTask(UArg arg0, UArg arg1)
1987 {

1989

1991  * Setup the PINMUX:
1992  * - GPIO Input : Configure pin J13 as GPIO_1 input
1993  * - GPIO Output: Configure pin K13 as GPIO_2 output
1994  **********************************************************************/

2015  while (1)
2016  {
2017  event = Event_pend(gMmwMssMCB.eventHandle,
2018  Event_Id_NONE,
2019  MMWDEMO_CLI_EVENTS | MMWDEMO_BSS_FAULT_EVENTS |
2020  MMWDEMO_DSS_EXCEPTION_EVENTS,
2021  BIOS_WAIT_FOREVER);
2022 
2023  /************************************************************************
2024  * CLI event:: SensorStart
2025  ************************************************************************/
2026 
2027  if(event & MMWDEMO_CLI_SENSORSTART_EVT)
2028  {
2029  System_printf ("Debug: MMWDemoMSS Received CLI sensorStart Event\n");
2030 
2031  /* Setup the data path: */
2032  if(gMmwMssMCB.isSensorStarted==false)
2033  {
2034  if (MmwDemo_mssDataPathConfig () < 0) {
2035  /* Post start failed event; error printing is done in function above */
2036  Event_post(gMmwMssMCB.eventHandleNotify, MMWDEMO_DSS_START_FAILED_EVT);
2037  continue;
2038  }
2039  else
2040  {
2041  /* start complete event is posted via DSS */
2042  }
2043  }
2044  else
2045  {
2046  /* Post start complete event as this is just a duplicate command */
2047  Event_post(gMmwMssMCB.eventHandleNotify, MMWDEMO_DSS_START_COMPLETED_EVT);
2048  continue;
2049  }
2050  }
2051 
2052  /************************************************************************
2053  * CLI event:: SensorStop
2054  ************************************************************************/
2055  if(event & MMWDEMO_CLI_SENSORSTOP_EVT)
2056  {
2057  if(gMmwMssMCB.isSensorStarted==true)
2058  {
2059  if (MmwDemo_mssDataPathStop () < 0) {
2060  /* Do we need stop fail event? */
2061  DebugP_assert(0);
2062  }
2063  else
2064  {
2065  /* DSS will post the stop completed event */
2066  }
2067  }
2068  else
2069  {
2070  /* Post data path stop complete event on behalf on Datapath in case sensor is already in stop state */
2071  Event_post(gMmwMssMCB.eventHandleNotify, MMWDEMO_DSS_STOP_COMPLETED_EVT);
2072  }
2073 
2074  /* In all cases send MSS stop complete */
2075  Event_post(gMmwMssMCB.eventHandleNotify, MMWDEMO_MSS_STOP_COMPLETED_EVT);
2076  }
2077 
2078  /************************************************************************
2079  * CLI event:: Framestart
2080  ************************************************************************/
2081  if(event & MMWDEMO_CLI_FRAMESTART_EVT)
2082  {
2083  /* error printing happens inside this function */
2084  if(gMmwMssMCB.isSensorStarted==false)
2085  {
2086  if (MmwDemo_mssDataPathStart () < 0) {
2087  /* Post start failed event; error printing is done in function above */
2088  Event_post(gMmwMssMCB.eventHandleNotify, MMWDEMO_DSS_START_FAILED_EVT);
2089  continue;
2090  }
2091  }
2092 
2093  /* Post event to start is done */
2094  Event_post(gMmwMssMCB.eventHandleNotify, MMWDEMO_DSS_START_COMPLETED_EVT);
2095  }
2096 
2097  /************************************************************************
2098  * BSS event:: CPU fault
2099  ************************************************************************/
2100  if(event & MMWDEMO_BSS_CPUFAULT_EVT)
2101  {
2102  MmwDemo_mssAssert(0);
2103  break;
2104  }
2105 
2106  /************************************************************************
2107  * BSS event:: ESM fault
2108  ************************************************************************/
2109  if(event & MMWDEMO_BSS_ESMFAULT_EVT)
2110  {
2111  MmwDemo_mssAssert(0);
2112  break;
2113  }
2114 
2115  /************************************************************************
2116  * BSS event:: Analog fault
2117  ************************************************************************/
2118  if (event & MMWDEMO_BSS_ANALOGFAULT_EVT)
2119  {
2120  MmwDemo_mssAssert(0);
2121  break;
2122  }
2123 
2124  if(event & MMWDEMO_DSS_CHIRP_PROC_DEADLINE_MISS_EVT)
2125  {
2126  CLI_write ("DSS Chirp Processing Deadline Miss Exception.\n");
2127  DebugP_assert(0);
2128  break;
2129  }
2130

2132  {
2133  CLI_write ("DSS Frame Processing Deadline Miss Exception.\n");
2134  DebugP_assert(0);
2135  break;
2136  }
2137  }
2138 
2139  System_printf("Debug: MMWDemoDSS Data path exit\n");
2140 }
